Barcelona star Lionel Messi says he need to be reminded of his hat-tricks . 
 The Argentine has netted 32 hat-tricks since making his debut in 2004 . 
 Messi's favourite came in a 3-3 draw against rivals Real Madrid in 2007 . 
 The 27 year old has had each of his hat-trick balls signed by team-mates . 
 